    {\displaystyle h({\mathcal {O}}(y,\psi ))=\{h\circ \psi (y,t):t\in \mathbb {R} \}=\{\phi (h(y),t):t\in \mathbb {R} \}={\mathcal {O}}(h(y),\phi )}
  for each 
  
    
      
