              x
            
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle f(x)=M^{-1}(x)g(h(x))\quad {\text{where}}\quad M(x)={\frac {\mathrm {d} h(x)}{\mathrm {d} x}}.}
  In that case, the dynamical systems can be transformed into each other by the coordinate transformation, 
  
    
      
